\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2.1}{\ignorespaces \small  CultureID's robot acting as a game master with pupils of the 4th public elementary school of Thessaloniki while on visit to the city's Archaeological Museum. The games' purpose is at the same time educational and entertaining. The robot requires from pupils to answer its questions, which they do by scouring the nearby exhibits for clues. A game consists of sets played at different museum sections, with the robot moving autonomously from one to the other among the pupils, while maintaining set distances from them and the museum's exhibits}}{9}{figure.caption.3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:cultureid_indy}{{2.1}{9}{\small CultureID's robot acting as a game master with pupils of the 4th public elementary school of Thessaloniki while on visit to the city's Archaeological Museum. The games' purpose is at the same time educational and entertaining. The robot requires from pupils to answer its questions, which they do by scouring the nearby exhibits for clues. A game consists of sets played at different museum sections, with the robot moving autonomously from one to the other among the pupils, while maintaining set distances from them and the museum's exhibits}{figure.caption.3}{}}
